      <p>In the case of the NCI-DREAM challenges, the final score was a weighted average of the
<italic>pc</italic>-index, which we termed the weighted, probabilistic c-index (
<italic>wpc</italic>-index), where the weights
<italic>w
<sub>d</sub></italic> for each drug
<italic>d</italic> reflect the quality of the measured data for
<italic>d</italic>, accounting for the range of total response and missing values. The
